<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.5.8">
<l>caṅkaiyun tuṇivum poyyum meyyumit taraṇi yōmpum</l>
<l>poṅkiya mukilu mallāp poruḷkaḷu māya ventai</l>
<l>paṅkaya mukutta tēṟal parukiya vāḷai pāya</l>
<l>ceṅkaya lukaḷum nāṅkūrt tirumaṇik kūṭat tāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Our father who, besides doubt and certainty, truth and lies,</l>
<l>And the swelling clouds which guard this earth, became all things,</l>
<l>Is the one in Tirumaṇikkūṭam in Nāṅkūr where rosy kayal [fish] frolic,</l>
<l>As vāḷai [fish], which sip the nectar that the lotuses shed, leap up.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
